race.description: Chaff Cutters Longford Cup NY Day Mdn Plate
race.comment: LUCKY COUNTRY (9) raced handy on debut and gave a big sight beaten just 0.9 lengths over 1200m at this track. He jumped a $2F off smart trials. There's plenty of improvement in store and he goes close with average luck from the awkward gate. Ditto ARIANNA'S GOLD (4), who resumed in the same contest beaten a nose. Had to skip over from the 9 gate and will likely jump from the same this evening. She also has more to offer. TASSIE POWER (2) resumes and two back just missed at Hobart over 1390m. Drawn to enjoy a nice trail just off the pace and is a chance if presented forward. ZANZI (7) resumes and can come back better. She's been close up in both recent trials and the race day betting will tell plenty with her.
